00:16:08,690 --> 00:16:09,650
Tianlei.

315
00:16:10,060 --> 00:16:12,740
♪The second sigh laments about the past♪

316
00:16:14,890 --> 00:16:15,620
Your Ladyship.

317
00:16:18,620 --> 00:16:19,890
I thought Du Bingyan

318
00:16:20,530 --> 00:16:21,100
