that she just walked right in.

322
00:16:29,020 --> 00:16:30,650
And she forced Tianlei

323
00:16:31,020 --> 00:16:32,810
to vow like that.

324
00:16:36,140 --> 00:16:37,810
This Third Young Mistress

325
00:16:38,020 --> 00:16:39,260
is quite something else.

326
00:16:42,530 --> 00:16:43,170
No hurry.

327
00:16:44,220 --> 00:16:45,930
Tianlei hasn't grown fond of me yet.

328
00:16:46,530 --> 00:16:49,340
I can't push this thing.

329
00:16:50,260 --> 00:16:51,740
Things will get tricky

330
00:16:52,380 --> 00:16:53,380
if we get on bad terms.

331
00:16:54,050 --> 00:16:55,340
This thing will take

332
00:16:55,980 --> 00:16:57,100
a lot of time and effort.

333
00:17:16,020 --> 00:17:18,020
Why are you so mad now?

334
00:17:18,220 --> 00:17:19,810
Weren't you quite generous just now?

335
00:17:20,220 --> 00:17:21,260
Who said I was generous?

336
00:17:21,290 --> 00:17:22,810
I'm the meanest one in the world.

337
00:17:22,810 --> 00:17:24,220
Qi Tianlei, be warned.

338
00:17:24,330 --> 00:17:25,290
If you like

339
00:17:25,290 --> 00:17:26,700
that pretty girl who's already ready to cry.

340
00:17:26,770 --> 00:17:28,130
Tell me in advance.

341
00:17:28,130 --> 00:17:28,740
I promise

