365
00:18:11,290 --> 00:18:12,810
How can you marry someone else?

366
00:18:13,290 --> 00:18:13,940
I won't allow it.

367
00:18:15,500 --> 00:18:16,330
You

368
00:18:16,810 --> 00:18:19,500
just go find your sweet Xiubo.

369
00:18:19,500 --> 00:18:20,740
Stop minding my business.

370
00:18:22,940 --> 00:18:24,220
Let's put everything else aside.

371
00:18:24,220 --> 00:18:25,050
Where did you get

372
00:18:25,050 --> 00:18:26,420
the so-called childhood sect brothers?

373
00:18:26,530 --> 00:18:27,530
Why haven't I heard of any?

374
00:18:27,570 --> 00:18:28,810
I've got plenty of

375
00:18:28,810 --> 00:18:29,700
childhood sect brothers.

376
00:18:29,700 --> 00:18:30,700
Why should I tell you?

377
00:18:33,130 --> 00:18:34,810
What are they called,
and where do they live?

378
00:18:34,940 --> 00:18:36,050
Are you still in touch with them?

379
00:18:36,330 --> 00:18:37,050
None of your business.

380
00:18:39,290 --> 00:18:40,020
Yeah.

381
00:18:40,500 --> 00:18:43,020
