382
00:18:43,260 --> 00:18:44,500
But Her Ladyship

383
00:18:44,610 --> 00:18:45,980
has a full house of

384
00:18:45,980 --> 00:18:47,050
sect brothers.

385
00:18:49,770 --> 00:18:51,980
You'd better comfort Her Ladyship now.

386
00:18:52,660 --> 00:18:53,530
Otherwise,

387
00:18:53,530 --> 00:18:54,700
she'd really pack her things

388
00:18:54,700 --> 00:18:56,130
and go back to Yangzhou
to marry someone else.

389
00:19:00,330 --> 00:19:01,570
Yes, you're right.

390
00:19:06,460 --> 00:19:07,660
My wife

391
00:19:08,020 --> 00:19:09,810
is as beautiful as a fairy.

392
00:19:10,500 --> 00:19:12,700
