397
00:19:22,940 --> 00:19:24,220
Save your pretty talk.

398
00:19:24,220 --> 00:19:25,290
I won't buy it.

399
00:19:26,940 --> 00:19:28,500
How can you not be mad, then?

400
00:19:30,660 --> 00:19:32,740
