00:20:22,330 --> 00:20:23,020
Are you ready?

422
00:20:23,020 --> 00:20:23,770
I'm ready.

423
00:20:24,220 --> 00:20:24,940
Catch.

424
00:20:32,130 --> 00:20:32,810
One more.

425
00:20:34,290 --> 00:20:34,940
This one.

