439
00:21:24,530 --> 00:21:25,500
Little glutton.

440
00:21:25,700 --> 00:21:26,740
This is your little punishment.

441
00:21:28,770 --> 00:21:29,460
Xiaoxi,

442
00:21:29,700 --> 00:21:30,570
please clean and dry

443
00:21:30,570 --> 00:21:32,460
all these plums.

444
00:21:33,130 --> 00:21:33,810
Remember,

445
00:21:33,810 --> 00:21:35,530
these are for Third Young Mistress.

446
00:21:35,530 --> 00:21:36,700
Nobody else is allowed to touch them.

447
00:21:37,180 --> 00:21:38,900
I'm gonna make wine personally
for my wife.

448
00:21:38,900 --> 00:21:39,810
Thank you, honey.

449
00:21:40,700 --> 00:21:41,900
Don't worry, Third Young Master.

450
00:21:42,130 --> 00:21:43,570
I'm gonna watch them myself.

451
00:21:43,700 --> 00:21:44,740
No one is gonna be missing.

452
00:21:45,900 --> 00:21:46,460
Let's go.

453
00:21:50,740 --> 00:21:51,290
Yummy, huh?

454
00:21:51,290 --> 00:21:52,330
It does taste sour.

455
00:22:01,130 --> 00:22:02,050
That tree

456
00:22:02,740 --> 00:22:05,420
was planted by Tianlei when he was young.

457
00:22:07,220 --> 00:22:08,460
Every year since then,

458
00:22:08,740 --> 00:22:10,740
