517
00:25:48,050 --> 00:25:50,220
Come on. Tell me now.

518
00:25:50,330 --> 00:25:53,090
It's just that Xiubo has a fever suddenly,

519
00:25:53,260 --> 00:25:54,740
and she can't eat anything.

520
00:25:54,980 --> 00:25:55,900
The doctor said

521
