545
00:26:47,850 --> 00:26:48,460
Xiaoqiao,

546
00:26:48,460 --> 00:26:49,660
go take a look over there.

547
00:26:49,660 --> 00:26:50,570
Tell Tianlei

548
00:26:50,700 --> 00:26:52,050
